quran[111]{c,v,t}:
  12,1,"Alɩf, Laam, Raa. Woto yaa Gaf vẽenegã Aayay-rãmbã."
  12,2,"Ad Tõnd sik-a lame, t'ɑ yɑɑ Alkʋrãan sẽn yɑɑ Laarabiimdu (goama), sẽn na yɩl n tɩ yãmb bãng ɑ võorã."
  12,3,"Tõnd togsda foom togsg sẽn yɩɩd neer sẽn tũ ne Tõnd sẽn tʋms wahɩ tɩ wa fo nengẽ wã, lɑ fo rɑ yɩɩme tɑoor t'ɑ na n pa sigi n yaa yam yaal-yaal soaba."
  12,4,"Tẽeg wakat ning A Yuusuf sẽn wa n yeel a saambã: ''m saamba, ad mam yẽnda ãds piig la a yembre, ne wĩndgã la kiuugã tɩ b maan maam suguudu''."
  12,5,"T'a yeele: ""m biiga, ra togs fo zãmsdã f saɑm-biisã ye, tɩ b wa maan foom rabr ye, ad a sʋɩtãan ne ninsaal yaa beem sẽn vẽnege."
  12,6,"Lɑ yaa woto bɑl la fo Soabã na n tũus foom, lɑ A wĩnig-f zãmsd welgre, la A pids A neemã wã fo zug la a Yaakuub zɑkã rãmb zugu, wala A sẽn da pids-a fo rogdb ɑ yiibã zug tɩ loogã, a ɭbraahɩɩm la a ɭshaaka. Ad fo Soabã yaa mit n yaa bʋʋd mita."
  12,7,"Sɩd la hakɩɩka, ad sagls be a Yuusuf ne a saam-biisã sʋk togsgã ne neb nins sẽn yaa sok-n-bãng rãmba."
  12,8,"B sẽn wa n yeele: "" ad tõnd baabã nonga a Yuusuf la a ma-biigã n yɩɩd tõndo, tɩ tõnd yaool n yɑɑ zãmɑ, ad tõnd baabã bee tudgr pʋgẽ sẽn yɑɑ vẽenega."
  12,9,"Kʋ-y-yã a Yuusuf maa y lobg-a tẽn-zãrgɑ, sẽn na yɩl n tɩ y saambã nengã wẽnems n tees yãmb bala, lɑ y lebg rẽ poorẽ n yɩ nin-sõma."
  12,10,"Tɩ b yembr yeele:"" ra kʋ-y a Yuusuf ye, lob-y-yã-a bulgã pʋgẽ, tɩ y sã nɑ n mɑɑnɑme, tɩ kẽnkẽndbã sãndɑ rɩkd-a lɑme""."
  12,11,"Tɩ b yeele: ""Yaa foo tõnd bɑ! Bõe n tar foom tɩ f ka basd a Yuusuf ne tõndo, tɩ tõnd yɑool n yɑɑ pʋ-beelem rãmb ne-ɑ."
  12,12,"Bɑs-ɑ ne tõnd beoogo t'a wãbdẽ la a reemdẽ tɩ d na n gũus-a lame""."
  12,13,"La a yeele: ""ad m sũur pɑ noom tɩ y tall-a n loog ye, lɑ m yεεsda katr na n wa wãb-a tɩ yãmb pa maan gũusg ne-ɑ ye""."
  12,14,"Tɩ b yeele: ""la tɩ katrã sã n wãb-a, tɩ tõnd yaool n yaa wʋsgo, rẽnd tõnd yɑɑ bõn-rãmb wε""."
  12,15,"Lɑ b sẽn wa n loog ne-a wã, n zems taab n na n lob-a bul-vulungã pʋga, tɩ Tõnd tʋm ɑ nengẽ: "" ad fo na n wɑ togsa bãmbã b yel-kãngã tɩ b pɑ ning b yɑmẽ tɩ yɑɑ foo ye."
  12,16,"Tɩ b wa b baabẽ wã zaabr n tar yãbre."
  12,17,"B yeelame:"" d baaba, ɑd tõnd kẽngame n tɩ maan reng-reng-tɑɑbɑ n bas a Yuusuf tõnd teedẽ wã tɩ katrã rɩ-a. Lɑ fo ka na n kõ tõnd sɩd ba tɩ tõnd sã n dɑ yɑɑ sɩd rãmbɑ."
  12,18,"Lɑ b bolg ɑ fuugã ne zĩri-beed zɩɩm. T'a yeele: "" yãmb yõyã sagla yãmb ne bũmb wẽnga, lɑ m nɑ mɑɑn sugr sẽn be neere! Lɑ m kota sõngr ne Wẽnd yãmb sẽn togsd yell ningã wã zugu!""."
  12,19,"Tɩ kẽnkẽndb wa n tʋm b ko-yõngdã t'a sik a lʋʋgã lɑ ɑ yeele: ad yaa sũ-noog wε! Wã yɑɑ biiga!"" La b solg-a n yeel tɩ yɑɑ lɑgo. La Wẽnd yɑɑ mit ne b sẽn maandã."
  12,20,"Tɩ b tʋg n koos-a ne ligd-yɑɑlgɑ: Wɑkɩr saar bala, lɑ b ra yɩɩme n yĩgsd ɑ koosgã."
  12,21,"Tɩ ned ning sẽn ra-a Misrɑ wã yeel a pagã: "" ges a sãandã sõma. Tõe t'a wa naf tõndo maa d rɩk-a n maan d biiga"". Lɑ yɑɑ woto me la Tõnd kõ a Yuusuf pãnga tẽngã pʋgẽ la sẽn nɑ yɩl tɩ D wĩnig-ɑ zãmsd-rãmb welgre, lɑ ad Wẽnd winda ne A sẽn rɑt yell ning fãɑ, la nebã sẽn waoog fãa pa mi ye."
  12,22,"La a sẽn wa n ta ɑ pãng tεkẽ, Tõnd kõ-a-la bʋʋd minim la bãngre, la yaa woto bɑl la D rond nin-sõmã wã."
  12,23,"Tɩ pag ning a sẽn be a soab zɑkẽ wã ro-ɑ ɑ meng yĩngɑ, n pag rɑgnoyã la a yeele: ""wa pɑɑm-mɑ!""- T'a yeele: ""Wẽnd na gũm-a! Ad mam zu-soabã mɑnegɑ mɑm zĩndgã, lɑ m kõn n zãmb-ɑ ye, ad wẽgdbã pa tõe n põs ye""."
  12,24,"Lɑ ɑd pagã mɑkɑme n nɑ n kẽ ne-ɑ, tɩ yẽ me rag n mɑmes ne-ɑ sã n pa a sẽn yã ɑ Soɑbã tɑgmasã. D mɑɑnɑ rẽ sẽn nɑ yɩl n zãag-a ne wẽngã la tʋʋm-beedã, ad a ra yɩɩme n be Tõnd yembs nins sẽn yɑɑ pʋ-peelem dãmbã pʋgẽ."
  12,25,"Tɩ b yiibã reng taab ragnoorẽ wã, tɩ pagã pãrg a fuugã poorẽ. Tɩ b sεg pagã zu-soɑbã ragnoorẽ wã, tɩ pagã yeele: "" ned ning sẽn ra tʋll fo zak rãmb ne wẽng rolb yaa bõe tɩ sã n pa b pɑg-ɑ maa sɩbgr sẽn zɑbde?"""
  12,26,"T'a yeele: ""yaa pagã n do mɑɑm m meng yĩngɑ"". Tɩ sεεt mɑɑn kɑset sẽn yi pɑgã nebẽ n yeele: ""sã n mikame t'a Yuusuf fuugã pãrga taoorẽ, bɩ y bãng tɩ pagã togsɑ sɩdɑ, t'a Yʋʋsuf yaa zĩri-be-neda."
  12,27,"La sã n mikame t'a fuugã pãrga poorẽ, rẽnd pagã yagda zĩri t'a Yuusuf lɑ sɩdã soɑbɑ"" ."
  12,28,"La a zu-soɑbã sẽn wa n yã t'ɑ fuugã pãrga poorẽ wã, a yeeleme: woto yaa yãmb pagb rabay! Ad yãmb rabay tar pãnga!"
  12,29,"Yuusufu bɑll n bas yel-kãngã goɑm! La fo (a pagã me) kos f beegrã yaafgo, ad f yɑɑ bεεgdɑ""."
  12,30,"Tɩ pɑgb yeel tẽngã pʋgẽ: "" Nim-bedrã pag rooda a yembã ɑ meng yĩngɑ! Ad a nonglemã kẽes-ɑ-lɑ bãɑgɑ. Ad tõnd getame t'a bee meneng pʋgẽ sẽn yɑɑ vẽenegɑ."
  12,31,"Lɑ pɑgã sẽn wa n wʋm b kɩɩsgã, a tʋmame tɩ b bool-ba, la a sεgl zĩig b yĩng n na maan rɩ-bendo; n kɩs ned fãa sʋʋg n yaool n yeele [ a Yuusuf]: ""yi tɩ b yã-fo"". Lɑ b sẽn wa n yẽ-a wã, b zẽka ɑ yellã (yel-solemde), n yirb n wã b nusã, lɑ b yeele: "" Wẽnd yɩlgame n yi lɑgem-n-tɑɑgɑ! Ad wãndã pa ned ye, wã pa yɩ rẽndɑme tɩ yaa malεk wɑgelle!''"
  12,32,"Tɩ pagã yeele: "" ad yãmb sẽn tar sãmbs ne maam a soab yĩngã la woto. Lɑ mam ro-a lɑme t'a zãgse. La a sã n pa sak mɑm sẽn sɑgend-ɑ wã, b na n pag-a lame, ɑ nɑ n yɩɩ yɑɑlgɑ."
  12,33,"T'a (Yuusuf) yeele: ""m Soaba, bãensã kõom n são bãmbã sẽn boond maam n tʋgd zĩig nĩngã, bɩ F peng mɑɑm n yi b rɑba wã tɩ m rɑ wa kɩll n tʋg b nengẽ n wɑ lebg zɩtbã yembr ye""."
  12,34,"T'a Soabã reeg a kosgã n wãnems-a n yiis b rabrã, ad Yẽ lɑ a Wʋmd n yaa a Bãngda."
  12,35,"Rẽ poorẽ tɩ b lebg n yã yellã sẽn vẽnegã poorẽ tɩ b na n pɑg-a lame n tãɑg wakat ninɑ."
  12,36,"Tɩ rɑsãmb a yiib naag-a n kẽ bãensã roogo, t'a yembrã yeele: ""mam zãmsame n kõgd sib-rãam"", t'a to wã yeele: ""mam zãmsame n tʋk bur m zugẽ wã, tɩ liuuli wã rɩt-ɑ; togs tõnd ɑ võorã tɩ ad tõnd neeme tɩ f yaa mɑnegdɑ""."
  12,37,"T'a yeele: "" rɩɩb pa wat n na n kõ yãmba, rẽndame tɩ mam reng n wĩniga yãmb a sẽn yaa a soaba, taoor t'a na n pa wa ye, rẽ me yɑɑ mam Soabã n wĩnig maam. Ad mam basa zãma sẽn pa kõt sɩd ne Wẽnd dĩin, tɩ bãmb yɑɑ kɩɩsdb ne Yɑoolem raarã."
  12,38,"La m tũuda m yaab-rãmbã dĩinã, a ɭbraahɩɩm la a ɭshaaka la a Yaakuuba, pa sõmb ne tõnd tɩ d maan lagem-n-taar baa fʋɩ ne Wẽnd ye, woto yaa Wẽnd yɩɩdlem A sẽn kõ tõnd la nebã fãɑ, la ɑd nebã sẽn waoog fãa pa pʋʋsd Wẽnd bark ye."
  12,39,"Yaa yãmb m bãens tũud-n-taas a yiibu! Soab-dãmb sẽn gɑl n yɩɩd ne sõmblem bɩɩ, bɩ Wẽnd sẽn yɑɑ Yembrã n yɑɑ Windã?"
  12,40,"Yãmb sẽn tũud bũmb ning zẽng sẽn pa Wẽndã pɑ zʋʋg yʋɩ bal yãmb la y yaab-rãmbã sẽn pʋd-bɑ, Wẽnd pa sik vẽenem b zug ye, ad bʋʋdã fãa gill yɑɑ Wẽnd n so, A sagla yãmb tɩ y ra tũ sã n pa Yẽnda, rẽndɑ la dĩin sẽn tẽeg tɩrga la ɑd nebã sẽn waoog fãa pa mi ye."
  12,41,"Yaa m bãens tũud-n-taas a yiibu! Sã n yɑɑ ne yãmb nin-yɛngã, ɑ na n yũnuga a zu-soabã rãam; la ned a to wã, b na n sãr-ɑ lame tɩ liuuli wã tɑr ɑ zugã n rɩtẽ. Yel ning yãmb sẽn sokd ɑ võorã pidɑme n nɑ n yɩ""."
  12,42,"La ɑ yeel ned ning a sẽn tẽed tɩ yẽ n na n põs b yiibã sʋkã "" tẽeg m yellã f zu-soabã nengẽ "". La a Sʋtãan yĩmsa yẽ a zu-soabã tẽegre, t'a Yuusuf ba bãensẽ wã yʋʋm-rãmbɑ."
  12,43,"Tɩ naabã yeele:"" sɩd la hakɩɩka, ad mam yãtɑ m zãmsdẽ nag-yãans a yopoe sẽn nobe tɩ nag-yãans sẽn yɑɑ wag a yopoe wãbd-ba, la kɑ-zut a yopoe sẽn yaa mɑɑs ne a taab sẽn yaa koeemse, togs-y mɑɑm m zãmsdã võor tɩ yãmb sã n mii zãmsd welgre''."
  12,44,"Lɑ a b yeele: ""ad yaa zãms-tulɑ! Lɑ tõnd rɑg n pa mi zãms-tul welgr ye''."
  12,45,"Tɩ sẽn põs-a b yiibã sʋkã yeele, ɑ sẽn tẽeg ɑ yellã wakat sẽn loog poorẽ:"" mam na n kõo yãmb a welgrã kibɑre, bi y tʋm maam!""."
  12,46,""" T'ɑ tʋg n tɑ n yeele : Yaa foo a Yuusuf sɩd soaba! Togds tõnd wã võore : nag-yãans a yopoe sẽn nob tɩ nag-yãan-wag a yopoe rɩt-ba, la ka-zut ɑ yopoe sẽn yaa mɑɑs ne ɑ taab sẽn yaa koeemse, tɩ m paam n leb nebã nengẽ sẽn na yɩl tɩ b bãng sẽn be a pʋgẽ."
  12,47,"T'a yeele:"" ko-y yʋʋm a yopoe n pʋg taaba ne nidg pãngɑ, tɩ y sẽn na n kẽebã fãa bĩng-y-yã-a ne a zutã, sã n ka bilf bal y sẽn na n rɩtẽ."
  12,48,"Rẽ loogr poorẽ, yʋʋm a yopoe n na n wa n yaa wɑre, tɩ y rɩt y sẽn dɑ ko n bĩng yʋʋm kεgengɑ yĩngã, sã n pɑ y sẽn nɑ n kell bilf sẽn yɑɑ bõn-buudu."
  12,49,"Rẽ loogr poorẽ, tɩgr yʋʋmd n na n wa, tɩ nebã kõtẽ lɑ b wẽkd tɩ-biisã lɑ b kõgda""."
  12,50,"Tɩ naabã yeele: "" sõng-y-m ne-ɑ"". La tẽn-tʋʋmã sẽn wa n wa ɑ Yuusuf nengẽ wã, ɑ yeelɑme:"" lebg n kẽng f zu-soabã nengẽ n tɩ soak-a: "" pagb nins sẽn wã b nusã kibɑrã yɩɩ wãn-wãnɑ? Ad mam Soabã n mi bãmb rɑbrã."
  12,51,"Tɩ (naabã) yeel (pagbã):"" yãmb yellã yɩɩ wãn-wãnɑ, yãmb sẽn wɑ n rood ɑ Yuusufã?"" Tɩ b yeele: "" Wẽnd yɩlg n yii lɑgem-n-tɑɑgɑ ! Tõnd pa bãng-a ne wẽng buud fãɑ ye"". Tɩ nim-bedrã pagã yeele: ""moasã sɩdɑ vẽnegame. Yaa maam n ro-a m meng yĩngɑ, lɑ ad a togsɑ sɩdɑ''."
  12,52,"Lɑ rẽ yɑɑ sẽn nɑ yɩl t'ɑ bãng tɩ m pɑ zãmb-a a kudgẽ ye, lɑ Wẽnd pa yãagd zãmb-rãmb rabsg ye."
  12,53,"Lɑ mam ka yɩlgd m yõorã, n yeel t'a yɩɩda wẽng mɑɑneg ye, ad yõorã pirsdame n tʋgd wẽnga, sã n pa ned ning m Soabã sẽn yols-ɑ, ad mam Soabã yaa yaafg naaba n yaa yolsg naaba""."
  12,54,"Tɩ naabã yeele: ""sõng-y-m ne-a tɩ m wεlg-a ne m mengɑ. Lɑ ɑ sẽn wa n gom ne-a wã, a yeelame: "" rũndã tεka fo bee tõnd nengẽ n yaa zĩnd-m-yɑm soɑbɑ n yɑɑ bas-yard soaba""."
  12,55,"T'a (Yuusuf) yeele: ""ning maam tẽngã bao zĩigẽ, tɩ ad mam yaa gũudɑ n yaa bãngda""."
  12,56,"Lɑ yaa woto la Tõnd kõ a Yuusuf pãng Misrɑ tẽngã pʋgẽ t'a zĩnd be a sẽn ratẽ, Tõnd paamsda D yolsgã Tõnd sẽn tʋll ne ɑ soɑbɑ, la D pa yeebd manegdbã keoor ye."
  12,57,"La ad yɑoolem-rɑɑr keoorã n yɩɩd sõmblem ne neb nins sẽn kõ-b sɩd lɑ b zoet Wẽndã."
  12,58,"T'a Yuusuf saam-biisã wa kẽ a nengẽ t'a bãng-ba la bãmb pa bãng-a ye."
  12,59,"La ɑ sẽn wa n sεglg b teedã n kõ-ba, a yeelame: "" zã-y a saam-biigã n wɑ poorẽ tɩ m kõ-y n pɑɑse, y pɑ ne tɩ mam pidsda vũgbã la m leb n yɩɩd sõmblem ne sãamd reegre?"
  12,60,"La yãmb sã n pa wa ne-a mam nengẽ, y pɑ tɑr vũgb mɑm nengẽ ye, pʋs n ra pẽneg-y maam ye""."
  12,61,"Tɩ b yeele: ""d na bõos ɑ ba wã, ɑd tõnd nɑ n mɑɑnɑ f sẽn dɑtã""."
  12,62,"T'a yeel a tʋʋmã koamba: ""lebs-y b ligdã b teedẽ wã, sãnd-sãnde b na bãng tɩ yɑɑ tõnd n so, b sã n wa lebg n tɑ b nebẽ wã, raare b na legb n wa''."
  12,63,"Lɑ b sẽn wa n lebg n tʋg b saambẽ wã, b yeelame: d saamba, ""b gɩdgɑ tõnd tɩ d sã n pɑ wɑ ne d sɑɑm-biigã b kõn n vũg n kõ-d ye. Bɩ f tũnug tõnd d saam-biigã sẽn na yɩl n tɩ d paam pʋlbo, ad tõnd na n gũ-a lame""."
  12,64,"T'a yeele: Rẽ yĩng m nɑ n maɑnɑ bɑs-m-yɑm ne yãmbɑ! Pɑ na yɩ wala mam sẽn ra mɑɑn bɑs-m-yɑm ne ɑ mɑ-biigã buud tɩ loogã? La Wẽnd la gũud sẽn yɩɩd sõmblem, lɑ Yẽ me n yɩɩd yoalsdbã fãa gill ne yolsgo."
  12,65,"La b sẽn wa n lɑgs b teedã, b mikam tɩ b lebs-b-lɑ b ligdã. Tɩ b yeele: ''Yaa foo d saamba! Bõe la tõnd le rata? Ad b sẽn lebs tõnd d ligdã. Tõnd na n leb n tɩ pʋlame n wɑ kõ d zɑgsã rãmb la d gũ d saam-biigã la d paas yʋgemd zɩlgre, ad vũg-kãngã yɑɑ nɑnɑ ne-ɑ""."
  12,66,"T'a yeele: ""mam pa na n tũnug-ɑ ne yãmb rẽndame tɩ yãmb rɩk sard mam taoor ne Wẽnd tɩ yãmb na n lebg n waa ne-a , sã n ka b wa n gũbga y fãɑ"". Lɑ b sẽn wa n rɩk b sardã a taoorã, a yeelame: ''Wẽnd la boabend ne tõnd sẽn yet bũmb ningã""."
  12,67,"T'a yeele : ''Yaa m koamba! Ra tʋg n kẽ-y noor a yembr ye, kẽ-y noe toor-toore. Lɑ mam pa tõe n naf yãmb baa fʋɩ n yi Wẽnd bʋʋdã pʋg ye. Yaa Yẽ la Mam bobl m menga, yaa Yẽ me lɑ bobl-m-meng rãmbã me sõmb n bobl b mense''."
  12,68,"Lɑ b sẽn wa n kẽ wala b saambã sẽn sagl-b to-to wã rẽ pa tõog n naf-b n yi Wẽnd bʋʋdã ye, ɑd yaa nimbãɑn-zoεεg sẽn be ɑ sũurẽ wã t'ɑ vẽneg-ɑ bɑlɑ, lɑ ad a tara bãngr ne rẽ, Tõnd sẽn karem-a yĩnga, la nebã wʋsg fãa pa mi ye."
  12,69,"Lɑ b sẽn wa n kẽ a Yuusuf nengẽ wã, a kɩll n wɑlmɑ ɑ ma-biigã n yeel-a: ""ad maɑm lɑ fo ma-biigã, bɩ f ra sãam f sũur ne b sẽn ra yɩ n maandẽ wã ye."
  12,70,"Lɑ, a sẽn wa n kõ-b b koodã, a ninga lɑ-vũgdgã a ma-biigã laogẽ, n yɑool n moond n yeele: ""Yaa yãmb ɑ toɑndbɑ! Ad yãmb yaa wagda""."
  12,71,"Tɩ b lebg n togl-b n yeele: ""yãmb bõe n meneme?"""
  12,72,"Tɩ b yeele: ""Tõnd gẽesda naabã la-vũgdga, lɑ ned ning sẽn wa ne-a ɑ tara yʋgemd zɩlgre, lɑ ɑ yɑoobã be ne maam""."
  12,73,"Lɑ b yeele: "" d wẽen ne Wẽnde, yãmb miime tɩ tõnd pa wa n na n sãam tẽngã pʋgẽ ye, d leb n pa yɩ n yɑɑ wagda""."
  12,74,"Tɩ b yeele: "" lɑ sẽn dɩk-ɑ wã sɩbgr yaa bõe yãmb nengẽ tɩ sã n mik tɩ yãmb yɑgdɑme?"""
  12,75,"Tɩ b yeele: "" ned ning b sẽn mik laagã a teedã pʋgẽ wã yẽ bɑl lɑ ɑ soɑb keoore t'ɑ soɑɑg-a, woto bɑl la wẽgdbã sɩbgre''."
  12,76,"[T'a Yuusuf] sɩng neb a taabã kordã veoosg n yaool n ta a ma-biigã nengẽ, rẽ poorẽ t'a yiis-a (laagã) a ma-biigã korgẽ, yaa woto la Tõnd wĩnig a Yuusuf rabr-kãngã, a rag n pa tõe n reeg a ma-biigã tɩ sã n yɑɑ naabã bʋʋd sɩbgr pʋgẽ, sã n pa Wẽnd n wɑ n tʋlle. Tõnd zẽkda ned ning dɑrgε Tõnd sẽn rata, lɑ bãngr soab fãa zugu, bãngd n be beenẽ."
  12,77,"Lɑ b yeele: sã n mikame t'a zuume, a ma-biig me n ra reng n zu"". ""T'a Yuusuf kel n wãb rẽ n vol n pɑ mɑɑn tɩ b bãng ye. A yeelɑ ɑ sũurẽ: ''yãmb sẽn be zĩig ningẽ wã wẽng n yɩɩde! La Wẽnd n yɩɩd minim ne kɩbɑr ning yãmb sẽn sɩfdã''."
  12,78,"Tɩ b yeele: Yaa foo tẽngã nin-kãsengɑ! Ad a tara saamb sẽn yaa nin-kẽem kʋdr n nong-ɑ wʋsgo, bɩ f reeg tõnd ned ɑ yembr ɑ zĩigẽ wã la f bas-a, ad tõnd neeme tɩ fo yaa nin-sõngo."
  12,79,"T'a yeele:"" Wẽnd na gũ-do, tɩ d ra wa yõk ned a to sã n pɑ d sẽn mik d bũmbã a soab nengẽ wã, sã n pɑ yɩ woto fãa, tõnd yɩta wẽgdba."
  12,80,"B sẽn wa n wãag b tẽebã, b lɑkɑme n leebd tɑɑb yɑm, tɩ b kãsem-soɑbã yeele: ""yãmb pa mi tɩ y saamb rɩkɑ sard yãmb zug ne Wẽnde; Yaa woto me tɩ yãmb rɑ reng n tall yɑm-kɑɑlg a Yuusuf nengẽ wã? Mam pa na n yẽrg tẽngã rẽndame tɩ m saamb kõ-m sore maa Wẽnd bʋ m yĩng tɩ m pɑɑm (yoslgo); Yẽ me la bʋ-kaoodb sẽn yɩɩd sõblem''."
  12,81,"Lebg-y n tʋg y baaba wã nengẽ n tɩ yeele: "" d baaba, ad fo biigã zuume, la tõnd ka maan kaset rẽnda ne tõnd sẽn bãngã bala, lɑ tõnd rɑ pa mi-ɑ ne wɑgdem ye."
  12,82,"La f sok tẽng ning tõnd sẽn da beẽ wã la kẽnkẽndb nins tõnd sẽn tũ n wɑ wã, lɑ sɩd la hakɩɩka ad tõnd togsa sɩda""."
  12,83,"La a (Yaakuub) yeele: ""yãmb yõyã le sagla yãmb ne yell ninga! Lɑ m maanda sugr sẽn be neere! Tõe tɩ Wẽnd wa ne b yiibã fãa gilli, ɑd Yẽnda la a Minim naab n yaa a Bʋʋd mita""."
  12,84,"La a tud-ba a zãn-kuidgã n yeele: ""m sũur sãam n tɑ tεk ɑ Yuusuf yĩnga!"" T'a ninã yiibã pelge, sũ-sãɑng kũnkũm yĩngɑ, tɩ sũ-toog rʋʋg-ɑ."
  12,85,"Tɩ b yeele: ''ne Wẽnde! Fo ka bak n tẽegd a Yuusuf yell halɩ tɩ fo wa bẽ maa f tolg n hɑlɑk ye""."
  12,86,"T'ɑ yeele: ""ad mam kũmda m sũurã lɑ m sũ-sãangã ne Wẽnde, la m mii Wẽnd nengẽ yãmb sẽn pa mi''."
  12,87,"Yaa m koambɑ! Kẽng-y n tɩ gẽes a Yuusuf ne a ma-biigã la y ra wãag y tẽeb ne Wẽnd yolsgã ye, ad pɑ wãɑgd tẽeb ne Wẽnd yolsgã rẽndɑ neb nins sẽn yɑɑ kɩfr-dãmbã."
  12,88,"La b sẽn wa n kẽ a (Yuusuf) nengẽ wã, b yeelame: "" tẽngã nin-bedre, ad kom n pɑɑm tõnd la d zakgs rãmbɑ; la tõnd waɑ ne lɑog sẽn yaa yɑɑlgɑ, bɩ f mak tɩ pid n kõ-do la f maan doɑag ne-do, ad Wẽnd nonga kõ-n-bɑo-yelsõm rãmbã."
  12,89,"Lɑ ɑ yeele: ''rẽ yĩnga yãmb bãngã (wẽgb) ning y sẽn maan a Yuusuf la a ma-biigã wɑkɑt ning yãmb sẽn dɑ wɑ n zɩ wã?''"
  12,90,"Tɩ b yeele: ""Rẽ yĩngã pɑ foo lɑ ɑ Yuusuf bɑlɑ!"" T'a yeele: ''ad yaa maam la a Yuusufu, la mam ma-biigã me la woto, ad Wẽnd mɑɑnɑ tõnd neere, ad ned ning sẽn zoet ɑ Wẽnd la a maan sugri, rẽnd Wẽnd pa yeebd manegdbã keoor ye''."
  12,91,"Tɩ b yeele: ''ne Wẽnde! Ad Wẽnd yɩɩga foom tõnd zugu, lɑ ad tõnd rɑ yɩɩme n yɑɑ yõsgdbɑ''."
  12,92,"T'a yeele: ""sãbsg ka be yãmb zug rũndã ye! Wẽnd na yaaf-ya, yaa Yẽ lɑ yolsdbã sẽn yɩɩd ne yolsgo''."
  12,93,"Kẽng-y ne mam fu-kãngã n tɩ pil m baabɑ nengã ne-ɑ: t'ɑ ninã na n pukɑme, la y wɑ ne y zagsã rãmb fãa mɑm nengẽ."
  12,94,"La (wakat ning) kẽnkẽndbã sẽn wa n gãndg Misrɑ toadgã, b saambã yeelame: ''ad mam yɑool n wʋmda ɑ Yuusuf yũugu, sã n pɑ yãmb sẽn na n wa yeel tɩ mam zʋbsdame wã''."
  12,95,"Lɑ b yeele: ''ne Wẽnd tɩ fo ket n bee f tuum-kʋdrã pʋgẽ''."
  12,96,"Lɑ sũ-noogdã sẽn wa n wɑ wã, ɑ lobɑ fuugã b bɑ wã nengã, t'ɑ lebg n neẽ, n yeele: ""mam pa yeel yãmb tɩ m mii Wẽnd nengẽ yãmb sẽn pa mi?"""
  12,97,"Tɩ b yeele: "" d baaba, kos Wẽnd t'a yaaf tõnd zunuubã, ad tõnd ra yɩɩme n yaa tudgdba""."
  12,98,"T'a yeele: ""m na wa n kos Wẽnd t'A yaaf-ya, ad Yẽ la yaafg naab n yaa yolsg naaba''."
  12,99,"Lɑ b sẽn wa n kẽ a Yuusuf nengẽ wã, a koka a rogdb ɑ yiibã lɑ ɑ yeel-ba: kẽ-y Misrɑ ne Wẽnd rɑɑbo, tɩ yãmb yɑɑ sẽn tar bɑs-m-yɑm'' ."
  12,100,"La a zẽk a rogdb ɑ yiibã naamã goeelã zugu, tɩ b lʋɩ n maan-a suguudu, t'a yeele: "" m saamba, ad mam pĩnd zãmsdã võor la woto, Wẽnd kɩtame t'a yɩ sɩdɑ, lɑ ɑd A maana maam neere, A sẽn yiis maam bãensẽ wã lɑ A yiis yãmb tẽn-kɩrengẽ wã n wɑ, sʋtãanã sẽn wa n kẽes yõs-taabã maam ne mam saam-biisã sʋkã. Mam Soabã sẽgsdɑ ne bũmb ning A sẽn rate, ad yaa Yẽ la minim naab n yaa bʋʋd mita''."
  12,101,"M Soaba! Ad fo kõo maam naam la F karem maan zãmsd wεgsgo, Foom la saas la tẽng naanda, Foom la mam lɑlldɑ dũni kaanẽ la yaoolem rɑɑrã, reeg mam yõorã tɩ mam yaa lɩslaama, la F naag maam ne nin-sõmã wã."
  12,102,"Woto yaa sẽn be kibay solgdsã pʋgẽ, tɩ Tõnd tʋm-ɑ fo nengẽ, lɑ fo rag n pa be b nengẽ b sẽn wa n zems taab n na n maan rabrã ye."
  12,103,"Lɑ nebã sẽn waoog fãa pɑ sɩd-kõtb ye, ba tɩ fo sã n mɑɑndɑ yã-beed ne rã."
  12,104,"Fo leb n pa kot-b yaood kãndagrã yĩng ye, ad ɑ pa yɩ rẽndame tɩ yaa tẽegr ne bõn-nɑɑndsã."
  12,105,"Lɑ sõor waoog tɑgmas-rãmb sẽn be saasẽ wã la tẽng zug tɩ bãmb pɩʋʋgd-b n pɑ ningd b toog ne-b ye."
  12,106,"Lɑ b wʋsgã fãa pɑ kõt sɩd ne Wẽnde, rẽndame tɩ b maand lagem-n-taar ne-A."
  12,107,"Rẽ yĩnga bãmbã paama bas-m-yam tɩ Wẽnd sɩbgrã pa na n wɑ bõr-bɑ, maa Wɑkɑtã pa na n ling-b n wɑ tɩ bãmb pa ning b yɑmẽ?"
  12,108,"Yeel-bɑ: ad woto yaa mam sor tɩ m boond nebã n tʋgd Wẽnd vẽenem zugu, maam la neb nins sẽn pʋgd maamã me boodɑme n tʋgd-A, lɑ yɩlgr be ne Wẽnde! Lɑ mam pa be legem-n-taarã rãmb pʋgẽ ye."
  12,109,"Lɑ tõnd pa tʋms sẽn reng foo taoore, rẽnda raopa, sẽn yi tẽn-bεdã pʋsẽ, tɩ Tõnd tʋmsd wahɩ wã tɩ kẽngd b nengẽ. Rẽ yĩngã b pa kẽnd tẽn-gãngã zug n tɑgsd n get neb nins sẽn reng bãmb taoorã baasg sẽn yɩ to-to? Ad yɑoolem-rɑɑr zɑkã n yɩɩd ne sõmblem ne neb nins sẽn zoet Wẽndã, yãmb pa nɑ n mɑɑn yɑm?"
  12,110,"Tɑrɑ boto hal tɩ tẽn-tʋmdbã sã n wa wãag b tẽeb ne nebã sɩdã kũuni, tɩ kɩfr-dãmbã wa tẽ tɩ b sẽn bugsd bãmbã yɑ zĩri, la Tõnd sõngrã sẽn wat tẽn-tʋʋmbã nengẽ, tɩ D põsg Tõnd sẽn tʋll n põsg-b rãmbɑ, la ɑd Tõnd nangã b pɑ tõe n tus-ɑ n yi nin-wẽnsã ye."
  12,111,"Ad bee bãmbã kibayã pʋgẽ tags-n-gesg ne pʋ-tẽ-nin rãmba, ad pa kibay sẽn wãag n rogl ye, la ad yaa Gɑf-rãmb nins sẽn reng tɑoorã sɩdgre lɑ bũmbã fãa welsgo, la kãndagr la yolsg ne neb sẽn kõt sɩdã."
